{"tid":1469384,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"回歸和理非","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:22:07.000Z","uid":86295,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72d1cf8b0dfaa3fd017287f94e79087917d591c9","tid":1469384,"uid":86295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:07.000Z","msg":"太多嘅升級活動，必然導致民意散渙。7婆已經打左開口牌，將個波推俾勇武。我明白好多人都想衝，但可唔可以用一個禮拜時間，回歸和理非？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以用番條勝利formula, 和理非，deadline，升級，而唔係keep住用街坊同遊客做擋箭牌？<br />\n<br />\n等一個禮拜時間，818，俾200萬和理非重新投入。"},{"pid":"01054829dc041a2740926b53fd63c28687ea6207","tid":1469384,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5538941f02e18d87ad2588b60c2c888d5d377d7","tid":1469384,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"2c8dce3e17a3dabc77dd692d415fb0974e145744","tid":1469384,"uid":86295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:22:07.000Z","msg":"818<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}